  "Description": {
    "English": "An exclusive <span class=\"name name-stellar\">starship</span>, retrieved while escaping the reality collapse that occurred during the <span class=\"name name-special\">Cursed Expedition</span>.<br><br><span class=\"name name-stellar\">Claim</span> this ship to add it to your collection, or <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Exchange</span> it with your current ship. While on a planet, summon ships from the Quick Menu<br>(<span class=\"name name-img\">QUICK_MENU</span>).",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一艘专属<span class=\"name name-stellar\">飞船</span>，这是你在<span class=\"name name-special\">被诅咒者远征</span>期间逃离不断崩塌的现实时找到的宝物。<br><br><span class=\"name name-stellar\">领取</span>这艘飞船，将它加入你的收藏，或与你现在的飞船<span class=\"name name-stellar\">交换</span>。在行星上时，使用快捷菜单<br>（<span class=\"name name-img\">QUICK_MENU</span>）召唤飞船。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "獨特的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">太空船</span>，在<span class=\"name name-special\">受詛咒之物探險</span>期間，逃離現實崩塌時回收所得。<br><br>可<span class=\"name name-stellar\">領取</span>並收藏這艘太空船，或是用目前太空船<span class=\"name name-stellar\">交換</span>。在星球上時，可用快捷選單 (<span class=\"name name-img\">QUICK_MENU</span>)<br>召喚太空船。"
  },
